{"tid":638752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【封鎖死傷？】中國遊客遊北韓遇「重大車禍」 傳巴士墮橋逾30死","createTime":"2018-04-23T03:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T04:11:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd9db584ace2ec5abfe7745cbcb696068a43d35","tid":638752,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"一班在北韓旅行的中國遊客周日晚在黃海北道遇上嚴重交通事故，導致中國遊客重大人員傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部已連夜啟動應急機制，駐朝使館工作組在朝外務省負責人陪同下火速趕赴事發現場，正在核實詳情。早前中國官方中央電視台英文頻道曾在社交網tweeter發文指有旅遊巴墮橋，造成逾30人死亡，但其後刪帖。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180423/58106810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F58106810&d=AAE0W%2Bi%2BPuItTZHlspz5jDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6ac698a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F58106810&h=77fa2cb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180423/58106810</a>"},{"pid":"8fbdb5f2c9dd7342ece016093aee294d8a3feac3","tid":638752,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bc3da634b6feb25eb7130864b5737e034345337","tid":638752,"uid":5335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a21741adbc2dacfb2113cdb5f7317dc4ae0051d1","tid":638752,"uid":33848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T03:57:42.000Z","msg":"今次可以點贏"},{"pid":"687ebece24d8f331afffb13b3d6af9ad9fcdf71b","tid":638752,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T03:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc774b75d5bfa2afcfa0b5953e3c8a18896594ee","tid":638752,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime